  <official_title>ULTRASOUND GUIDED POPLITEAL SCIATIC NERVE BLOCK USING BUPIVACAINE ALONE OR COMBINED WITH MAGNESIUM SULFATE FOR DIABETIC FOOT SURGERIES</official_title>
